data.description: Welcome to your new haven at 8906 Bill Hickcock in the serene Texas Oaks community! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers an inviting open floor plan, complemented by soaring vaulted ceilings and an abundance of natural light that dances across the room. Elegant tile flooring spans the entirety of the living, dining, and kitchen areas, ensuring a seamless transition and easy maintenance. The bathrooms have been thoughtfully renovated, featuring contemporary fixtures and finishes for a sophisticated modern appeal.  Staying connected is a breeze with high-speed Google Fiber internet, perfect for both leisure and remote work. Retreat to the master bedroom, a tranquil sanctuary with a picturesque long bay window, rich wood floors, and a generous walk-in closet.  Step outside to the private backyard where majestic oak trees provide a cool canopy of shade. The built-in fire pit is the ideal spot for gatherings or quiet evenings under the stars. And when it's time to venture out, you're just a short drive away from HEB, Dutch Bros Coffee, and a variety of dining options. Embrace the blend of comfort and convenience at this delightful Texas Oaks residence!
